    {
        "content": "<p>Oh you said it yourself:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Bar</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Foo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">deriving</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Inhabited</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>should work</p>",
